{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.1","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 9:1","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.009.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Bienveillance de David envers Mephiboscheth, fils de Jonathan<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-13: cf. 1 S 20. (2 S 4:4; 16:1-4; 19:24-30.) Pr 10:7. Lu 14:12-14.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.9.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>David dit: Reste-t-il encore quelqu\u2019un de la maison de Sa\u00fcl, pour que je lui fasse du bien \u00e0 cause de Jonathan?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9","name":"2 Samuel 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.2","name":"2 Samuel 9:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.18","name":"2 Samuel 8:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.2","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 9:2","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.009.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.009.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.9.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il y avait un serviteur de la maison de Sa\u00fcl, nomm\u00e9 Tsiba, que l\u2019on fit venir aupr\u00e8s de David. Le roi lui dit: Es-tu Tsiba? Et il r\u00e9pondit: Ton serviteur!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9","name":"2 Samuel 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.3","name":"2 Samuel 9:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.1","name":"2 Samuel 9:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.3","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 9:3","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.009.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.009.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.9.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Le roi dit: N\u2019y a-t-il plus personne de la maison de Sa\u00fcl, pour que j\u2019use envers lui de la bont\u00e9 de Dieu? Et Tsiba r\u00e9pondit au roi: Il y a encore un fils de Jonathan, perclus des pieds.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9","name":"2 Samuel 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.4","name":"2 Samuel 9:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.2","name":"2 Samuel 9:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.4","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 9:4","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.009.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.009.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.9.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Le roi lui dit: O\u00f9 est-il? Et Tsiba r\u00e9pondit au roi: Il est dans la maison de Makir, fils d\u2019Ammiel, \u00e0 Lodebar.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9","name":"2 Samuel 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.5","name":"2 Samuel 9:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.3","name":"2 Samuel 9:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.5","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 9:5","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.009.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.009.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.9.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Le roi David l\u2019envoya chercher dans la maison de Makir, fils d\u2019Ammiel, \u00e0 Lodebar.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9","name":"2 Samuel 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.6","name":"2 Samuel 9:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.4","name":"2 Samuel 9:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.6","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 9:6","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.009.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.009.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.9.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Et Mephiboscheth, fils de Jonathan, fils de Sa\u00fcl, vint aupr\u00e8s de David, tomba sur sa face et se prosterna. David dit: Mephiboscheth! Et il r\u00e9pondit: Voici ton serviteur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9","name":"2 Samuel 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.7","name":"2 Samuel 9:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.5","name":"2 Samuel 9:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.7","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 9:7","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.009.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.009.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.9.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>David lui dit: Ne crains point, car je veux te faire du bien \u00e0 cause de Jonathan, ton p\u00e8re. Je te rendrai toutes les terres de Sa\u00fcl, ton p\u00e8re, et tu mangeras toujours \u00e0 ma table.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9","name":"2 Samuel 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.8","name":"2 Samuel 9:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.6","name":"2 Samuel 9:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.8","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 9:8","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.009.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.009.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.9.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Il se prosterna, et dit: Qu\u2019est ton serviteur, pour que tu regardes un chien mort, tel que moi?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9","name":"2 Samuel 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.9","name":"2 Samuel 9:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.7","name":"2 Samuel 9:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.9","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 9:9","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.009.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.009.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.9.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Le roi appela Tsiba, serviteur de Sa\u00fcl, et lui dit: Je donne au fils de ton ma\u00eetre tout ce qui appartenait \u00e0 Sa\u00fcl et \u00e0 toute sa maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9","name":"2 Samuel 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.10","name":"2 Samuel 9:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.8","name":"2 Samuel 9:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.10","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 9:10","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.009.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.009.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.9.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Tu cultiveras pour lui les terres, toi, tes fils, et tes serviteurs, et tu feras les r\u00e9coltes, afin que le fils de ton ma\u00eetre ait du pain \u00e0 manger; et Mephiboscheth, fils de ton ma\u00eetre, mangera toujours \u00e0 ma table. Or Tsiba avait quinze fils et vingt serviteurs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9","name":"2 Samuel 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.11","name":"2 Samuel 9:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.9","name":"2 Samuel 9:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.11","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 9:11","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.009.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.009.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.9.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Il dit au roi: Ton serviteur fera tout ce que le roi mon seigneur ordonne \u00e0 son serviteur. Et Mephiboscheth mangea \u00e0 la table de David, comme l\u2019un des fils du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9","name":"2 Samuel 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.12","name":"2 Samuel 9:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.10","name":"2 Samuel 9:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.12","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 9:12","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.009.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.009.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.9.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Mephiboscheth avait un jeune fils, nomm\u00e9 Mica, et tous ceux qui demeuraient dans la maison de Tsiba \u00e9taient serviteurs de Mephiboscheth.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9","name":"2 Samuel 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.13","name":"2 Samuel 9:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.11","name":"2 Samuel 9:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.13","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 9:13","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.009.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.010.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.9.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Mephiboscheth habitait \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, car il mangeait toujours \u00e0 la table du roi. Il \u00e9tait boiteux des deux pieds.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9","name":"2 Samuel 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.10.1","name":"2 Samuel 10:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.10.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.12","name":"2 Samuel 9:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb8d0aff4.89502056');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb8d0aff4.89502056\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb8d0aff4.89502056","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb8d0aff4.89502056'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb8d0aff4.89502056\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}